{"tid":856171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港過多十年可能連外國網都上唔到","createTime":"2018-10-10T12:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T18:13:52.000Z","uid":176910,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"988a49c44b0c36fa5590f9ebb5e024924364b199","tid":856171,"uid":176910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:23:59.000Z","msg":"高鐵、港豬澳大橋、三跑呢啲大白象只要政府一意孤行強行推廣過咗一排就會沒人理。個個返工嘅返工，移民嘅移民，基本上大家都對香港沒哂希望。但對中共嚟講，香港嘅言論自由始終都係眼中釘，大陸政權依家仲維持到好多都係靠佢嘅網絡長城幫手去控制信息，就好似六四咁，其實好多大陸後生嘅都知六四咩事，但佢哋接收到嘅資料就係嗰陣嘅學生全部出嚟搞事，死係應該，最好全家一齊死。<br />\n依家政府可以敢出個一萬億嘅人工島方案，咁一個限制上網、言論自由嘅方案佢又點會唔敢推出呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5afa04a6c9f28a2481366db91863e01b5af00b","tid":856171,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c57e64f17ee922dca4e2b5938c7facc18bdfac","tid":856171,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5460130bb23979009f268f532f9302c3f2fd58","tid":856171,"uid":197920,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:07:50.000Z","msg":"等睇十年內以下事件逐樣發生<br />\n<br />\n23條立法：<br />\n所有影響國家（黨）的言論、報章都要收皮<br />\n禁蘋果日報言，係蘋果賣廣告等於犯法<br />\n<br />\nDse中文強制用普通話考：<br />\n等反共唔學普通話既唔洗入大學<br />\n<br />\n社會信用評給：<br />\n批評國家同政府既唔比買機票<br />\n<br />\n中資全面佔據香港：<br />\n反黨=工都唔洗返<br />\n<br />\n網絡實名制：<br />\n連登、高登，facebook批評黨就等比人捉<br />\n<br />\n最後，等香港人冇哂利用價值就起集中營：<br />\n圈養港豬"},{"pid":"c9a899eb3d2875bc65790803b6f3e4c957cb1b4a","tid":856171,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:08:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ceed2a8613a170c6a0faa9b9053a6a2cc359bb3","tid":856171,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"十年之後支那仲喺唔喺度都成問題"},{"pid":"8078a5ef827b31e278b5b9371acec0b8017484d9","tid":856171,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"香港已死咪好事，"},{"pid":"c3cbc555d168224f1006936e5a15cd464aba7789","tid":856171,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:10:06.000Z","msg":"今年佢鎖國鎖埋香港，仲十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0c2316ba0d8f38cf1a89ed2c1e08a194f6dd88","tid":856171,"uid":197920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ceed2a8613a170c6a0faa9b9053a6a2cc359bb3","tid":856171,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"十年之後支那仲喺唔喺度都成問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:10:25.000Z","msg":"有港豬送成萬億上去，又吊多幾年命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec291e73e100e90f6588020fda581a460203bae","tid":856171,"uid":150807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"無所謂12年後可能香港陸沉呢"},{"pid":"3fcf6bfe805a2e1cac41b7aaa918d4b5f32ae0b0","tid":856171,"uid":65858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:11:23.000Z","msg":"呢幾年已經完唔唔比面 戲都唔演下 話批就批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01b227b60fd13789bd0c887ec3aaac329e410e3","tid":856171,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fcf6bfe805a2e1cac41b7aaa918d4b5f32ae0b0","tid":856171,"uid":65858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:11:23.000Z","msg":"呢幾年已經完唔唔比面 戲都唔演下 話批就批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:15:23.000Z","msg":"無所謂架,班讚成派議員都係有好多香港人去選出黎"},{"pid":"611709ba5052bae7f8c334d668597f5d95c88ed4","tid":856171,"uid":65858,"like":0,"di