.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果依家真係推出網絡長城一定好大反彈，但依家日日溫水煮蛙緊，到時真係俾政府推行到都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395aa059fb8d037b620507a07331e0c57efd964b","tid":856171,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:53:14.000Z","msg":"沒有google只有百度 沒有youtube 只有bilibili <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f3ff9893ef6420da808d462f1887a131f173af","tid":856171,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b0c2316ba0d8f38cf1a89ed2c1e08a194f6dd88","tid":856171,"uid":197920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ceed2a8613a170c6a0faa9b9053a6a2cc359bb3","tid":856171,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"十年之後支那仲喺唔喺度都成問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:10:25.000Z","msg":"有港豬送成萬億上去，又吊多幾年命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T18:13:52.000Z","msg":"你估人仔變廢紙先定呢１兆上左去先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}